Firmware Binary License (TODO: finalize terms before GA)
=========================================================

TODO: When prebuilt firmware binaries are shipped in this directory, the
actual terms must be finalized by the product/legal team.

- If the firmware is closed-source or governed by a separate EULA, state
  the user rights and redistribution restrictions here or in an `EULA` file
  in the same directory.

- If the firmware is released under an open-source license, replace this
  file with the full license text and note the SPDX identifier and version
  in [README.md](README.md).

Until the terms are finalized, do not interpret this text as granting any
binary distribution rights; the formal legal text at the time of release
shall prevail.
